    "body": "It's an implementation detail that we represent `0xffffffffffffffff` as `Infinity`. We require the epoch to be a quoted base-10 number eg `\"18446744073709551615\"`\r\n\r\nDefinitely a bug tho to accept `\"Infinity\"` without throwing on config validation.",
