    "body": "> The Infinity values should be parsed as Infinity.\r\n\r\nThis is not expected behaviour. Arguments parser should throw if it parses a number as NaN. Consumers should specify `18446744073709551615` not `Infinity`, see  https://github.com/ethereum/consensus-specs/blob/d8e74090cf33864f1956a1ee12ba5a94d21a6ac4/configs/mainnet.yaml#L49\r\n",
